{"tid":2367260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"土耳其總統接種中國科興的疫苗","createTime":"2021-01-15T07:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T08:38:06.000Z","uid":54800,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0d7cfe808bf377e51f65c782ce2be154825fa3ed","tid":2367260,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"土耳其開始為醫護人員，接種由中國科興生物研製的新型冠狀病毒疫苗，總統埃爾多安亦在安卡拉接種首劑疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其訂購了5000萬劑科興疫苗，並已經取得當中300萬劑，雖然在土耳其的測試中，疫苗有效率九成一，但試驗人數只有29人。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部長呼籲民眾盡快接種疫苗，表示是戰勝疫情大流行的最重要方法。"},{"pid":"acd0391e2259928376960afc0b373ea138ae7951","tid":2367260,"uid":54800,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"鄭月哦女仕幾時帶頭打返支科興疫苗？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc590a05c024f12cc3a461715fbcc8abd41df057","tid":2367260,"uid":13663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"疫苗有效率九成一，但試驗人數只有29人😌"},{"pid":"bea9e7c65523a20c6d453d6f9a832f4926c56da6","tid":2367260,"uid":268429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T08:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等睇中東大反擊.."},{"pid":"17182f8a068a977444fa55bd3a6d4527e1b13578","tid":2367260,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T08:01:24.000Z","msg":"習近平：又多一隻白老鼠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8132b28f0c3ae27503dffda82c06c75cb7746fc","tid":2367260,"uid":76848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc590a05c024f12cc3a461715fbcc8abd41df057","tid":2367260,"uid":13663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:59:07.000Z","msg